com.vmware.vcenter.deployment

Interface Migrate

  • All Superinterfaces:
    MigrateTypes, Service
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MigrateStub

    public interface Migrate
extends Service, MigrateTypes
    The Migrate interface provides methods to configure the migration of this appliance from an existing vCenter for Windows. This interface was added in vSphere API 7.0.0.

      • get

        MigrateTypes.MigrateSpec get()
        Get the MigrateSpec parameters used to configure the ongoing appliance migration. This method was added in vSphere API 7.0.0.

        Synchronous method overload. Result of the invocation will be reported as a method return value.

        Returns:
        MigrateSpec parameters being used to configure appliance migration.
        Throws:
        Unauthenticated - if the caller is not authenticated.
        NotAllowedInCurrentState - if appliance is not in MIGRATE_PROGRESS state.
